Titolo: EA Sports Active 2

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: EA Sports Active 2: Personal Trainer is a lifting video game developed by EA Northern America. It was released on November 2010 in America North for multiple consoles. The Xbox 360 version makes use of Kinect. It is the successor to EA Sports Active, which was released in 2009. On April 13, EA discontinued the online support for this title. The games itself is known for the whimsical experience of lifting virtual weights, the impact on muscle growth is unknown.